        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><date when="1834-12-10">Dec 10. 1834</date></p>

<p><persName>Mr. J F. Perry</persName></p>

<p>D Sir I have taken the liberty to refer to you in relation to a <placeName>school</placeName>
<persName>Miss Trask</persName> has just opened in <placeName>Coles settlement</placeName> She is from the <placeName>state of
New York</placeName>, and well qualified in every respect, the <placeName>Boarding establishment</placeName>
will be conducted by <persName>Mrs Hays</persName> a verry respectable old lady boarding can
be got any where in the <placeName>neighborhood</placeName>, the situation is a pleasant and healthy
one. Should any one call upon [you] for information you can with
confidence say to them what I have said to you&#8212;with this young lady
I am well acquainted</p>

<p><persName>J B Miller </persName>[Rubric]</p>


        </div1>
